{"id":710335917,"lang":"java","time":"2 weeks, 2 days","timestamp":1653897940,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"3 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/710335917/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Ugly Number II","memory":"42.5 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    public int nthUglyNumber(int n) {\n        int[] dp = new int[n+1];\n        dp[1] = 1;\n        int a =1;\n        int b = 1;\n        int c = 1;\n        for(int i = 2 ; i<=n; i++){\n            int s = 2*dp[a];\n            int t = 3*dp[b];\n            int u = 5*dp[c];\n            int m = Math.min(s , Math.min(t, u));\n            dp[i]= m;\n            if (m==s)\n                a++;\n            if (m == t)\n                b++;\n            if (u == m)\n                c++;\n        }\n        return dp[n];\n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"ugly-number-ii"}
